{"id": 2041, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年给爸妈买东西，你都有什么心得？", "description": "如今看到什么样的东西，你会觉得“啊！这好适合我爸妈！”（题图来自：   GIPHY)", "record_count": 1785, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171130173652SjNDhn3VG6MsaEvL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-06T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 252929, "content": "不敢再像以前做买点贺卡了，羞得拿不出手。买点吃的，或是中药补身子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205461}, {"id": 257537, "content": "事先征求父母意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208400}, {"id": 252930, "content": "我想大概是买个女朋友吧，如果买的到的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942319}, {"id": 252931, "content": "我爸说象棋差对象,让我哪天带个回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070657}, {"id": 253187, "content": "每次见面都会亲妈妈的脸颊或者拥抱，让她活在满满的爱意里。每年都会写一份感恩信给她，努力赚钱为了将来能给她一个房子再买一个门面做她自己想要做的，完成她自己的职业梦想。大大小小的礼物经常送给她，你要不停地用爱去滋润她，她会越来越年轻，这是爱一个人的全部体现吧！在这个世界上她是我的唯一", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166636}, {"id": 252932, "content": "多送一点自己的时间给他们", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986954}, {"id": 252933, "content": "?被说，霍生！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 252935, "content": "多陪伴父母是真的，树欲静而风不止，子欲养而亲不待", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205486}, {"id": 252936, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": "img/option/option/20171206223424mj1dhQi9bx4CSV3v.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182699}, {"id": 252937, "content": "易上手的手机...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150776}, {"id": 252938, "content": "sbnsjs", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150776}, {"id": 252939, "content": "不错还爸爸把", "image": "img/option/option/20171206223532qvkG3iEYlOXyMjV1.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182699}, {"id": 252940, "content": "我摸摸OL监控默默", "image": "img/option/option/20171206223604ceLzrUbxm3vgK0XY.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182699}, {"id": 252941, "content": "当然是带一厚叠钞票咯    ????", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200341}, {"id": 252942, "content": "好多人都去买莎普爱思了吧。。。大概?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 254222, "content": "直接给红包，简单干脆，他们就爱这种", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845968}, {"id": 254478, "content": "只要是用心挑的大概他们都会笑的开怀吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213720}, {"id": 252944, "content": "永远不能报原价！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205525}, {"id": 252948, "content": "把我带回家。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176254}, {"id": 254237, "content": "买点什么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112740}, {"id": 252958, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841030}, {"id": 253470, "content": "母上从小就是精致的猪猪女孩啊…会把链接发给我拍的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208425}, {"id": 252959, "content": "爸妈最想我们多点留在他们身边", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205588}, {"id": 252960, "content": "妈妈小年生日，这么多年没变过的就是一个蛋糕一瓶酒，爸妈都很开心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110944}, {"id": 252961, "content": "不会报原价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205608}, {"id": 252963, "content": "买什么，家里旧的永远比新的好用。买的新的慢慢都变旧了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205625}, {"id": 252965, "content": "每月给存钱，换季给买衣服鞋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202527}, {"id": 252967, "content": "男盆友", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205699}, {"id": 252972, "content": "可以远程的手机。每次视频手舞足蹈的形容，依旧不懂我在说什么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205715}, {"id": 252974, "content": "1他们一直挂在嘴边的，买给他们准没错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145289}, {"id": 252976, "content": "带对象回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919562}, {"id": 252977, "content": "Smartisan品牌手机，可以解决父母电子产品远程协助的需求，联系有此需求的同学试试", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094649}, {"id": 252978, "content": "女朋友。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130873}, {"id": 252979, "content": "买东西回家：买这个干啥，家里都有；你买的什么质量，我哪哪哪买的比这好。离家走了：这个这个这个还有这个，都拿着，你在外面太难。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131220}, {"id": 252980, "content": "一定要注意父母对什么不能用。给我妈买了一只口红 ，结果她用了过敏。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770585}, {"id": 252981, "content": "1", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1149729}, {"id": 252982, "content": "千万别买保健品，会让他们觉得自己老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981141}, {"id": 253245, "content": "买个对象回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195418}, {"id": 253254, "content": "按摩仪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206989}, {"id": 254790, "content": "对于我妈这种淘宝比我凶，每天抱手机时间比我长，不用护肤品不穿金戴银不养花不热爱小动物对带娃没兴趣的人，我每年都很苦恼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088900}, {"id": 253001, "content": "周黑鸭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927905}, {"id": 253522, "content": "多沟通，多理解，多陪伴。\n新颖的东西，更简便的让他们熟悉了解甚至使用。方便他们的生活。\n给他们买东西，总是要发生不愉快，我忍。平时慢慢开导。\n异乡求学，一年在他们身边的时间不到四分之一。\n祝所有父母，健康快来", "image": "img/option/option/20171210181552urmwQ2qYZ8A9nESc", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1143716}, {"id": 257625, "content": "买之前和售货员说好我妈不喜欢这个款式可以换吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227767}, {"id": 256348, "content": "对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221869}, {"id": 263530, "content": "遇到合适的就买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254208}, {"id": 253290, "content": "刚给爸妈买了护膝和护腰，该保暖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207218}, {"id": 253043, "content": "卖吃的 从来不踩雷！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869548}, {"id": 253047, "content": "买什么都嫌贵...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1183312}, {"id": 252029, "content": "想给爸妈买辟谣日历，“不是每天都必须喝八杯水”", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 252030, "content": "如果有《丝巾free沙滩摄影指南》，该给我妈来一本，希望她在跨年朋友圈摄影大赛玩得开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}